    "translations": {
      "en": {
        "summary": "Imam al-Baqir (AS) instructed Abu Hamza al-Thumali on the correct approach to the station of Imam Ali (AS), warning against both diminishing and exaggerating his rank. He highlighted two unique eschatological roles: leading battle during the Raj'a (the Return before Judgment Day) and uniting Paradise's inhabitants in marriage.",
